Seems not Enough Liberties but...
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par It is not good to solve only difficult problems, so sometimes it is good to get confidence through easy ones.
\par
\par However nobody should underestimate a problem which looks too easy.
\par
\par Save the White stones without any trouble.
\par
\par
\par }
