Dia. 01 Not Enough Liberty
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If it would be possible to win the capturing race with a move like White 1, this shape wouldn't be published as a problem.
\par After Black 2, White has \cf1\b simply not enough liberty\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par
\par
\par }
