Dia. 02 Thoughtless Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is a \cf1\b thoughtless move\cf0\b0 .
\par After Black answers with 2, White's defeat becomes obvious.
\par
\par Black has three liberties while White has only 2.
\par
\par
\par }
