Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's hane with 1 on the first line is the \cf1\b maek\cf0\b0  which is aiming at Black's shortage of liberties.
\par Black has to play at 2 and if White plays the dansu at 3, Black has no answer left. If White plays at A instead of 3 White wins the capturing race again.
\par
\par }
